00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:27,260
It's sweet.

520
00:30:27,260 --> 00:30:29,369
- But not too sweet, right?
- Yeah.

521
00:30:29,369 --> 00:30:30,629
It's refreshing.

522
00:30:30,630 --> 00:30:33,651
- Let me get you some more tea. Here you go.
- Sure.

523
00:30:33,651 --> 00:30:36,810
<i>Thank you, Xiaochun.</i>

524
00:30:36,810 --> 00:30:39,370
<i>Thank you.</i>

525
00:30:39,370 --> 00:30:41,519
You can make yourself at home here. Don't be a stranger.

526
00:30:41,519 --> 00:30:43,330
Okay.

527
00:30:46,580 --> 00:30:50,820
♫ <i>The sun will rise and fall</i> ♫

528
00:30:57,080 --> 00:31:02,020
♫ <i>It's just another day</i> ♫

529
00:31:23,710 --> 00:31:26,390
Feel free to look around and find something you might need.

530
00:31:27,300 --> 00:31:29,760
Did you make all the crafts here?

531
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:33,589
Nope. My master and the other craftsmen in the village sell them here after they carve them.

532
00:31:33,589 --> 00:31:36,490
I'm just a rookie with a few years of experience. I can't make such masterpieces.

533
00:31:44,910 --> 00:31:46,570
What's that?

534
00:31:47,150 --> 00:31:49,640
I carved it for fun.

535
00:31:51,390 --> 00:31:53,290
It's interesting.

536
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:56,200
Really?

537
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:58,890
This woman looks furious,

538
00:31:58,890 --> 00:32:00,690
but also rather comical.

539
00:32:00,690 --> 00:32:02,380
Who is she?

540
00:32:02,380 --> 00:32:04,020
My older sister.

541
00:32:04,710 --> 00:32:06,340
Your older sister?

542
00:32:07,230 --> 00:32:09,500
She looks like my older sister.

543
00:32:11,780 --> 00:32:14,050
- Did you come over from the cafe next door?
- Yeah.

544
00:32:14,050 --> 00:32:16,420
You share a yard anyway.

545
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:18,890
My sister runs that cafe.

546
00:32:18,890 --> 00:32:20,299
Is Xie Xiaochun your sister?

547
00:32:20,300 --> 00:32:21,629
Do you know my sister?

548
00:32:21,630 --> 00:32:24,639
I rented a room here. I just arrived yesterday.

549
00:32:24,639 --> 00:32:26,890
Oh, you're the new tenant at the courtyard.

550
00:32:26,890 --> 00:32:28,660
I'm Xie Xiaoxia.

551
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:30,340
I'm Xu Hongdou.

552
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:34,910
Xu Hongdou.

553
00:32:36,580 --> 00:32:39,330
You can have this for fun.

554
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:42,430
- Thank you.
- It's nothing.

555
00:32:42,430 --> 00:32:43,990
- Come over when you're free.
- Okay.

556
00:32:43,990 --> 00:32:45,600
Bye-bye.

557
00:34:07,100 --> 00:34:11,980
