558
00:34:14,260 --> 00:34:19,640
♫ <i>Enjoy the mountainous landscape at sunset</i> ♫

559
00:34:21,540 --> 00:34:28,279
♫ <i>The raindrops from the roof drip into my eyes quietly</i> ♫

560
00:34:28,279 --> 00:34:33,740
♫ <i>The world is like a quiet island</i> ♫

561
00:34:37,020 --> 00:34:39,890
You should know the way now. Make sure to visit us again.

562
00:34:41,250 --> 00:34:42,250
Here you go.

563
00:34:42,250 --> 00:34:45,279
Thank you, Sister Xiaochun. I'm so glad to meet you. I'll definitely come again.

564
00:34:45,279 --> 00:34:47,179
This is our new tea.

565
00:34:47,180 --> 00:34:48,890
You must try it.

566
00:34:48,890 --> 00:34:49,869
Thank you for the gift.

567
00:34:49,870 --> 00:34:50,869
Bye-bye.

568
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:52,619
You're welcome. Come again when you have the time.

569
00:34:52,620 --> 00:34:54,679
- Take care.
- Okay.

570
00:34:55,390 --> 00:34:56,900
Do come again!

571
00:34:56,900 --> 00:34:58,600
Bye-bye.

572
00:35:01,830 --> 00:35:03,850
Are you keen on Ms. Li?

573
00:35:03,850 --> 00:35:05,619
Yes.

574
00:35:05,620 --> 00:35:07,309
I think Ms. Li is great.

575
00:35:07,310 --> 00:35:09,030
How about marrying her?

576
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:11,989
You make it sound like she'll marry me once I propose.

577
00:35:11,990 --> 00:35:13,369
She's not interested in me.

578
00:35:13,369 --> 00:35:14,569
How can that be?

579
00:35:14,569 --> 00:35:17,050
If she's not interested in you, why did she want to add you on WeChat?

580
00:35:17,050 --> 00:35:19,659
Listen up. Now that you added her on WeChat,

581
00:35:19,660 --> 00:35:21,490
you should talk to her more often.

582
00:35:21,490 --> 00:35:23,829
Make friends with her first.

583
00:35:23,830 --> 00:35:26,300
Ms. Li is really nice.

584
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:28,320
Yes, she is.

585
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:29,909
As for Xia Xia...

586
00:35:29,910 --> 00:35:32,790
Don't change the subject!

587
00:35:32,790 --> 00:35:34,019
I got it.

588
00:35:34,020 --> 00:35:35,309
I've added her on WeChat.

589
00:35:35,310 --> 00:35:36,649
She's a nice woman.

590
00:35:36,649 --> 00:35:38,539
We can be friends first.

591
00:35:38,540 --> 00:35:40,939
Don't try to placate me. Make sure you take the initiative.

592
00:35:40,939 --> 00:35:42,039
Okay.

593
00:35:42,039 --> 00:35:43,349
So, what about Xia Xia?

594
00:35:43,350 --> 00:35:45,930
Why is he suddenly heading to Shanghai?

595
00:35:45,930 --> 00:35:48,440
Did my mom tell you?

596
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:52,090
Recently, he got to know a friend in Shanghai.

597
00:35:52,090 --> 00:35:55,189
He was invited over, so he wants to meet up with his friend.

598
00:35:56,180 --> 00:35:57,289
A friend from Shanghai?

599
00:35:57,289 --> 00:35:58,579
Male or female?

600
00:35:58,580 --> 00:35:59,539
He said the friend is male.

601
00:35:59,540 --> 00:36:01,690
They made friends while playing video games.

602
00:36:01,690 --> 00:36:03,429
But I doubt so.

603
00:36:03,430 --> 00:36:07,499
These days, he takes his phone with him to the bathroom.

604
00:36:07,499 --> 00:36:11,270
I'm guessing he's dating someone online.

605
00:36:12,430 --> 00:36:16,370
So, Xia Xia has reached the age for dating.

606
00:36:16,370 --> 00:36:17,989
My mom doesn't share this opinion.

607
00:36:17,990 --> 00:36:22,480
She thinks Xia Xia wants to get a job in Shanghai.

608
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:26,120
In that case,

609
00:36:26,120 --> 00:36:29,340
you can't stop him anymore since he's an adult.

610
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:31,959
If he wants to have fun in Shanghai, let him go.

611
00:36:31,959 --> 00:36:35,070
If he's determined to find a job there,

612
00:36:35,070 --> 00:36:36,920
then let him go ahead.

613
00:36:38,390 --> 00:36:42,810
But... his master has been in a terrible mood lately.

614
00:36:42,810 --> 00:36:45,649
A few years ago, his son insisted on venturing into machine carving.

615
00:36:45,649 --> 00:36:48,849
He was so furious that his high blood pressure acted up and he had to be hospitalized.

616
00:36:48,849 --> 00:36:52,519
Later, he was given the title of the state inheritor of intangible cultural heritage.

617
00:36:52,519 --> 00:36:53,699
He felt the need to pass on his craft.

618
00:36:53,700 --> 00:36:55,660
So, he took in a dozen apprentices.

619
00:36:55,660 --> 00:36:59,620
In the end, these apprentices slowly left.

620
00:36:59,620 --> 00:37:02,519
Xia Xia is the one who has learned from him for the longest time.

621
00:37:02,519 --> 00:37:03,869
Besides, they're from the same village.

622
00:37:03,870 --> 00:37:05,219
So, they're related in a sense.

623
00:37:05,220 --> 00:37:07,850
He pays quite a lot of attention to Xia Xia.

624
00:37:07,850 --> 00:37:10,230
If Xia Xia leaves him,

625
00:37:10,230 --> 00:37:11,930
I'm worried he won't be able to take it.

626
00:37:11,930 --> 00:37:14,300
He can't, but he has to.

627
00:37:14,300 --> 00:37:16,360
My granny once said this.

628
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:18,280
Times have changed.

629
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,699
Deeply buried gold cannot shine.

630
00:37:19,700 --> 00:37:21,809
The platform for traditional handicrafts is shrinking.

631
00:37:21,809 --> 00:37:24,989
If people are unaware of such valuable things, there won't be a market for them either.

632
00:37:24,990 --> 00:37:26,600
His apprentices have picked up his craft,

633
00:37:26,600 --> 00:37:28,349
but they can't make any money.

634
00:37:28,350 --> 00:37:30,180
They have no choice but to leave.

635
00:37:30,180 --> 00:37:31,770
You're right.

636
00:37:31,770 --> 00:37:34,140
Even when you offered to market his pieces,

637
00:37:34,140 --> 00:37:37,200
he even rejected you because he thinks advertisements are lies.

638
00:37:39,390 --> 00:37:43,489
How about this? I'll invite Xia Xia over for dinner tonight and talk to him about this.

639
00:37:44,690 --> 00:37:46,219
Thank you, Brother.

640
00:37:46,220 --> 00:37:47,800
Anytime.

641
00:37:58,870 --> 00:38:00,099
This is uneven.

642
00:38:00,100 --> 00:38:01,500
I'll show you.

643
00:38:04,020 --> 00:38:05,489
Look carefully. Okay.

644
00:38:05,489 --> 00:38:09,329
Take as many pictures as you can. These can be used for advertisement.

645
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:13,909
You should start embroidering there.

646
00:38:13,910 --> 00:38:16,630
Yes, only then will the color be uniform.

647
00:38:18,170 --> 00:38:20,500
You can lower this a little.

648
00:38:22,660 --> 00:38:25,519
<i>Mommy! Mommy! I caught a butterfly.</i>

649
00:38:25,519 --> 00:38:26,829
<i>A'Yao.</i>

650
00:38:26,830 --> 00:38:30,249
<i>Butterflies are beneficial insects that can spread pollen to help crops grow.</i>

651
00:38:30,249 --> 00:38:32,180
<i>Set it free.</i>

652
00:38:33,580 --> 00:38:35,339
<i>A'Yao, come here.</i>

653
00:38:35,339 --> 00:38:37,269
<i>I'll make you a hat with a lotus on it.</i>

654
00:38:37,270 --> 00:38:39,829
<i>I don't want a lotus. Only girls have flowers on their hats.</i>

655
00:38:39,829 --> 00:38:41,750
<i>Well, what do you like?</i>

656
00:38:42,750 --> 00:38:43,950
<i>A butterfly.</i>

657
00:38:43,950 --> 00:38:46,540
<i>Okay, I'll embroider a butterfly. Come over.</i>

658
00:38:49,950 --> 00:38:52,210
Okay. Cut. It's a wrap.

659
00:38:52,210 --> 00:38:55,689
- Ms. Xie, thank you for your hard work. Thank you.
- It's nothing.

660
00:38:55,689 --> 00:38:57,309
- Let's take a picture together.
- Sure.

661
00:38:57,309 --> 00:38:59,409
- Let me take a picture for you!
- Join us.

662
00:38:59,431 --> 00:39:00,919
Join us, Chairman Xie.

663
00:39:00,919 --> 00:39:02,870
I don't want to butt in.

664
00:39:02,910 --> 00:39:04,810
Guys, hurry up.

665
00:39:05,350 --> 00:39:07,800
Look at the camera. Let me adjust it a little bit.

666
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:10,430
Okay. One, two, three.

667
00:39:10,430 --> 00:39:11,499
Done.

668
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:12,430
Okay. Thanks a lot.

669
00:39:12,430 --> 00:39:13,820
Anytime. Take care.

670
00:39:13,820 --> 00:39:15,350
Okay.

671
00:39:15,350 --> 00:39:19,039
- Director Liu, I'll send you the materials via email after I export them tonight.
- No problem.

672
00:39:19,039 --> 00:39:21,000
I need to discuss something else with you.

673
00:39:23,540 --> 00:39:27,039
Director Liu, does your TV station have a program for wood carving?

674
00:39:27,039 --> 00:39:28,309
I have someone to recommend to you.

675
00:39:28,310 --> 00:39:29,699
A municipal inheritor of intangible cultural heritage.

676
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:31,429
He was given the title even earlier than Ms. Xie,

677
00:39:31,430 --> 00:39:34,670
but he's a veteran craftsman who keeps a low profile.

678
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:37,290
We just went to Jianchuan last month.

679
00:39:39,020 --> 00:39:41,489
- It's fine.
- There may be opportunities in the future.

680
00:39:41,489 --> 00:39:42,549
- Sure.
- Talk to you next time.

681
00:39:42,549 --> 00:39:44,330
No problem.

682
00:39:47,960 --> 00:39:49,530
Okay. I'll see myself out.

683
00:39:49,530 --> 00:39:51,429
- Gezi, please walk Director Liu out.
- Okay.

684
00:39:51,429 --> 00:39:52,140
- See you.
- Bye-bye.

685
00:39:52,140 --> 00:39:54,070
- Let me take this for you.
- Take care.

686
00:40:09,350 --> 00:40:11,120
Have they left?

687
00:40:11,620 --> 00:40:13,030
Aunty,

688
00:40:13,030 --> 00:40:15,559
you had an exhausting day. Go home early and get some rest.

689
00:40:15,559 --> 00:40:16,649
I'm not tired.

690
00:40:16,649 --> 00:40:19,020
I didn't even do any physical labor.

691
00:40:20,310 --> 00:40:23,270
When they were filming just now,

692
00:40:23,270 --> 00:40:27,589
I was thinking that if Mom didn't give up on embroidery to work,

693
00:40:27,589 --> 00:40:31,900
she would be with you on the show right now.

694
00:40:31,900 --> 00:40:33,869
If your mom didn't work,

695
00:40:33,870 --> 00:40:36,390
