696
00:40:37,060 --> 00:40:38,889
I didn't have a child to raise.

697
00:40:38,889 --> 00:40:40,640
Otherwise, I would've left the village

698
00:40:40,640 --> 00:40:44,210
to work with your mom.

699
00:40:45,830 --> 00:40:48,240
Do you miss your mom?

700
00:40:51,870 --> 00:40:55,519
You were still in junior high school when your mom passed away.

701
00:40:55,519 --> 00:40:58,650
It's been 20 years now.

702
00:40:58,650 --> 00:41:00,370
How time flies.

703
00:41:21,620 --> 00:41:22,870
A'Yao,

704
00:41:22,870 --> 00:41:24,960
