711
00:41:39,130 --> 00:41:40,869
Take a shower before you eat.

712
00:41:40,870 --> 00:41:43,480
You stink! You're gross!

713
00:41:45,700 --> 00:41:48,340
I've washed my hands.

714
00:41:49,930 --> 00:41:51,389
Why did you kick me?

715
00:41:51,389 --> 00:41:52,880
Shower.

716
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:54,780
Granny!

717
00:41:54,780 --> 00:41:58,229
It's fine to scold him, but why did you beat him?

718
00:41:58,229 --> 00:42:00,720
Granny, you can't pamper him.

719
00:42:00,720 --> 00:42:02,619
You didn't treat me like this when I was a child.

720
00:42:02,620 --> 00:42:04,209
We're living in different times.

721
00:42:04,209 --> 00:42:06,729
Beating others isn't right. It's uncivilized.

722
00:42:06,729 --> 00:42:09,600
Yes, uncivilized.

723
00:42:10,990 --> 00:42:13,829
You've had enough fun at home.

724
00:42:13,830 --> 00:42:16,400
It's time for you to go back to school in Kunming.

725
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:17,469
Did you hear what Granny said?

726
00:42:17,470 --> 00:42:19,949
She wants you to return to school in Kunming.

727
00:42:19,950 --> 00:42:21,169
You've stayed at home for a month.

728
00:42:21,169 --> 00:42:23,990
If you don't go back to school, you won't be able to keep up.

729
00:42:25,540 --> 00:42:27,700
I don't want to go back.

730
00:42:27,700 --> 00:42:30,350
You have to attend school!

731
00:42:30,350 --> 00:42:32,629
Granny! I don't want to go to school!

732
00:42:32,629 --> 00:42:35,169
I want to stay here. I want to rear horses.

733
00:42:35,169 --> 00:42:36,909
Brother, you can venture out for your career.

734
00:42:36,910 --> 00:42:39,190
I'll stay here and take care of Granny.

735
00:42:39,190 --> 00:42:40,949
You need someone to serve you all three meals

736
00:42:40,950 --> 00:42:42,499
