737
00:42:42,500 --> 00:42:44,999
You scamper around the village like a stray dog and no one can find you.

738
00:42:44,999 --> 00:42:46,720
How can you take care of Granny?

739
00:42:46,720 --> 00:42:48,949
That's because you're around and I'm not needed.

740
00:42:48,950 --> 00:42:50,590
Right, Granny?

741
00:42:51,390 --> 00:42:53,309
Why did you kick me again?

742
00:42:53,310 --> 00:42:55,400
Granny!

743
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:57,579
Why did you hit him again?

744
00:42:57,580 --> 00:43:00,820
Granny, you won't let me hit him, but why did you hit me?!

745
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:04,159
I didn't hit you. I just tapped you lightly.

746
00:43:04,159 --> 00:43:06,690
Right. A light tap.

747
00:43:06,690 --> 00:43:08,810
I'm sorry, Brother!

